          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
            How to  <br/>
            <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-pink-500">merge videos online?</span>
          </h2>

          <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Don't waste hours uploading huge files just to stitch them together. 
            <br/><br/>
            <strong>FastVideoCutter</strong> acts like a magnetic timeline, letting you combine unlimited video clips directly in your browser. Just drag, drop, and snap them into place.
          </p>

          <!-- Highlights Grid -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            {highlights.map(item => (
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800/80 p-3 rounded-xl">
                <span class="text-xl">{item.icon}</span>
                <span class="font-bold text-slate-300 text-sm">{item.label}</span>
